Percy Maimela has created the largest coffee sketch in the world. JOHANNESBURG - South African artist Percy Maimela is a Guinness World Record holder after creating the largest coffee sketch in the world. The 33-year-old created a picture of popular South African DJ Black Coffee using nothing but coffee. READ: Rich Mnisi wins Essence Emerging Designer of the Year award “This was my first experiment with coffee and it came out perfect. I love what I do, whatever goes on in my mind it’s magic, I actually talk to the art, but I couldn’t because it’s public”, said Maimela. Maimela dedicates his achievement to every South Africa who is scared of chasing their dream The coffee sketch is at Sandton City until Saturday. Percy Maimela has created the largest coffee sketch in the world. Courtesy #DStv403